cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.HC 

This paper involves the use of reinforcement learning and decision-making models to control autonomous vehicles in a mixed traffic environment. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with safety constraints and human behavior, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) respectively.
